pite CPU staying seemingly unchanged.\n\n3. **Ad Service Client Errors**\n   - **Metric Key**: `client_error_ratio`, `error_ratio`\n   - **Component**: adservice-0\n   - **Reason**: While the error ratio stayed at 0.0, the P99 change ratio indicates issues at peak loads potentially affecting clients.\n   - **Evidence**: P99 for client error ratio doubled from 1.62 to zero during failure period.\n\n### Key Hypotheses\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"server_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"High increase in server_error_ratio during fault time which affects user access.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"server_error_ratio surged from 0.0 to 30.24\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant growth in error_ratio indicating response processing failures.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"error_ratio increased from 0.0 to 29.16\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max remains high potentially prolonging transaction times.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max fault median at 7985.0 despite stable pod_cpu_usage\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Peak P99 change in client_error_ratio hints at failure during load spikes.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"client_error_ratio P99 doubled during fault time.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n此次分析揭示了系统中多个服务组件在故障期间遭遇了不同程度的异常，这些异常可能是导致系统中断的关键原因。请结合具体日志进一步诊断。"}
