"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend service experienced elevated 'server_error_ratio', 'error_ratio', and 'rrt_max' indicating potential network communication issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"server_error_ratio increased from 0.0 to 30.24 (frontend-0), error_ratio similarly high across all frontend pods.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 下一步建议\n与网络团队进行沟通，检查 **frontend** 服务的加载均衡与网络配置，确保服务间通信的稳定性。同时，考虑是否需要调优 **frontend** 服务的其他资源配置以减少错误影响。"}
